data.description:
JUST REDUCED! It may not reflect on the system yet. we are at $179,900. 
 Come see this meticulously maintained 3 bedroom 2 bath home in a very quiet area of Cape Coral. Upon entry, you will notice the open-inviting kitchen along with the great floor plan that allows for lots of light in every room. The kitchen boasts newer appliances and a large breakfast bar, perfect for entertaining or a quick snack. The  large spacious family room has sliders to the back screened lanai making it easy to experience the Florida lifestyle and enjoy bug free meals outside.  Feel free to bring a boat with plenty of parking on side of home it will be easy access for hitching up quick and off to the boat ramp. There is room for a pool as well. Easy access to I-75; Southwest Florida International Airport; fantastic shopping and the world renowned beaches of Southwest Florida. Great for the investor or to create your own family memories!
data.whatILove: Love this quiet neighborhood tucked back in the NE of Cape Coral. Life changes are pushing us to move elsewhere but this is one amazing home and place to live.
